WEBVTT

00:02:57.800 --> 00:03:02.759
One thing I learned at the Golden
Temple was to be thankful to everyone.

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:07.560
People who lift you, but more importantly
people who try to put you down.

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:10.560
(Applause)

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:16.159
Because when they try to oppress you,
your strength is revealed.

00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:20.279
You have no idea how 
you manage to overcome all that.

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:26.439
For instance, 1893 is a very
important year for the whole world.

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:30.479
A conductor made Gandhi ji
get off the train in South Africa.